txt.en: You have been tasked with thwarting Angmarim bat-keepers in Gundabad.
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Ausma for your reward!

'I have a new mission for you, [placeholder].\n\n'My scouts have returned from an Angmarim keep in the mountains of Gundabad. There they have spotted a group of Angmarim who breed and train bats. Their vile tactics can not stand! We must return to the keep, defeat the bat-keepers, and put an end to their nefarious breeding!'

Some monsters in this mission will attempt to lay down traps that will give you a debuff if caught in the trap.
Your mission is to thwart Angmarim bat-keepers in Gundabad.\n\nSpeak to Ausma to travel.
'Well done! With the bat-keepers defeated, we now have one less thing to worry about when traversing the dark caverns of Gundabad! I would recant the others if the list were not so long!'
